{"tid":1000033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求巴絲推薦Taplet  （返學讀書用）","createTime":"2019-01-29T06:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T09:32:22.000Z","uid":213807,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a885691da975663f5925314faf257e706778a0f0","tid":1000033,"uid":213807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"講講我既背景先<br />\n<br />\n而家讀緊PT，返學既地邊同學校都幾遠（成個鐘車程）<br />\n唔想放工帶埋一堆Hard Copy Notes返學所以一直想買部Taplet代替<br />\n市面上聯想，Apple，Samsung各大牌子實在太多選擇喇。<br />\n既然用得黎讀書梗係要有支筆寫下Notes啦<br />\n但小弟係一個百分之一百有選擇困難症既人。<br />\n想問下巴打而家用緊邊部Tablet，有無好推薦呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a3c25d6295b69ba0ea14ac554a07dceeb714e2","tid":1000033,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"窮撚買Ipad 2018<br />\n有錢買ipad pro"},{"pid":"6379975615d33e2b56b5a11134a33cd78410acad","tid":1000033,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36a3c25d6295b69ba0ea14ac554a07dceeb714e2","tid":1000033,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"窮撚買Ipad 2018<br />\n有錢買ipad pro"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"記得買埋枝筆"},{"pid":"81985d8db1625cf4f7cf233c977ed220abc98a92","tid":1000033,"uid":24310,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"您是不是要查： Tablet"},{"pid":"6c5dccef71c34983efbd106769d471d73be52b78","tid":1000033,"uid":213807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6379975615d33e2b56b5a11134a33cd78410acad","tid":1000033,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36a3c25d6295b69ba0ea14ac554a07dceeb714e2","tid":1000033,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"窮撚買Ipad 2018<br />\n有錢買ipad pro"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"記得買埋枝筆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"買埋支筆好貴呀🙈"},{"